06:10.338 --> 06:20.229
But what I did, I remember that very first credentialing interview, as God was pouring into my life, he was calling me in the ministry, and he was positioning me for such a time as this.

06:20.329 --> 06:22.832
Little did I know that I would be here eventually.

06:22.912 --> 06:35.186
I remember that first credentialing interview, and as I sat across the desk, there were three precipitors or higher officials in our district that were sitting there, and they began to

06:35.586 --> 06:41.213
really challenged me in that calling and the future of what I felt God had.

06:41.273 --> 06:45.418
And they asked me this question, son, I want you to know today.

06:45.478 --> 06:48.502
This is how they talked in the 90s.

06:49.163 --> 06:51.386
Brother, I just want to, I want to check with you today.

06:51.466 --> 06:56.812
What is your call in the God has placed upon your life and where are you headed in ministry?

06:57.713 --> 07:01.358
Those of you who have been part of this and with the God, how many of you will testify in the 90s?

07:01.558 --> 07:02.539
