07:40.381 --> 07:42.450
Because we are his church.

07:43.842 --> 07:49.107
He said, God, Jesus said, I will build my church and the gates of hell will not prevail against it.

07:49.127 --> 07:57.655
Upon this massive rock, this foundation, I will build a church that the gates of hell are powerless against.

07:57.915 --> 08:02.099
Listen carefully, church, we have to make ourselves available to God.

08:02.299 --> 08:05.182
