Well, Jesus, as you come out of the Gospels, Matthew, Mark, Luke, and John, we read the fact that Jesus died on the cross, he rose from the grave, he ascends back to heaven, but before he ascends to heaven, he tells the early believers, he says, go to Jerusalem and wait for the promise.

