39:41.917 --> 39:44.480
We're considering the cost we've processed through.

39:44.500 --> 39:49.324
We've actually modified, originally, if you remember, the building went out into the lower field.

39:50.906 --> 39:53.328
We realized that that was not cost effective.

39:53.869 --> 39:58.573
That was going to cost us, truth be told, about $180,000 to move dirt.

40:00.515 --> 40:03.578
As a board, we did not feel that was being wide stewards.

40:04.418 --> 40:08.242
We would rather put $180,000 into a building

40:08.354 --> 40:09.535
rather than moving dirt.

40:10.676 --> 40:10.957
Yes?

40:11.877 --> 40:18.244
So therefore we're moving this direction and then that direction, we will stop right at that drop off.

40:18.864 --> 40:23.769
They'll modify some of that so that we take parking on down into that area.

40:23.809 --> 40:25.671
So what's gonna happen with parking?

40:25.691 --> 40:29.995
We'll have temporary parking, they'll establish parking with gravel.

40:30.235 --> 40:32.257
So during the construction time, we'll have a place to park.

40:32.718 --> 40:35.861
Truth number two, the early church accepted the challenge.

40:35.881 --> 40:37.202
They consider the cost

40:37.378 --> 40:39.721
and they accepted the challenge.

40:40.102 --> 40:41.804
Now let's take a moment and look at the early church.

40:42.265 --> 40:49.935
It says, all the believers were united in heart and mind, and they felt that what they owned was not their own.

40:50.796 --> 40:53.300
So they shared everything they had.

40:55.923 --> 41:04.094
The apostles testified powerfully to the resurrection of the Lord Jesus, and God's great blessing was upon all of them.

41:05.036 --> 41:06.898
There were no needy people among them.

41:07.234 --> 41:14.022
But those who owned land and houses would sell them and bring the money to the apostles to give to those in need.

41:14.042 --> 41:15.844
Let me give you a little relief today.

41:15.864 --> 41:16.565
You ready for this?

41:17.406 --> 41:21.570
I am not asking you to sell your house and give all the money to the church.

41:23.092 --> 41:25.054
You guys are like, oh, praise God.

41:26.276 --> 41:27.617
Yeah, I'm not asking that.

41:28.558 --> 41:29.579
That's what the early church did.

41:29.599 --> 41:30.380
That's how they function.

41:30.400 --> 41:31.081
That's what they did.

41:31.882 --> 41:35.346
I'm just simply asking you, consider the cost and rise to the challenge.

41:35.874 --> 41:36.835
So let's talk cost.

41:36.855 --> 41:38.056
What's the overall cost?

41:38.096 --> 41:39.858
What have we raised and what do we need?

41:40.719 --> 41:42.441
These are three vitally important questions.

41:43.162 --> 41:44.523
First, what's the cost?

41:44.824 --> 41:50.690
The building construction, just for the building itself, is $4.35 million.

41:50.850 --> 41:59.940
And then we add to that $500,000 for audio, visual lighting and finishes, all the interior stuff.

41:59.980 --> 42:05.266
So it'll all end cost of $4.85 million.

42:05.378 --> 42:06.239
for this expansion.

42:07.742 --> 42:08.002
Wow.

42:11.047 --> 42:12.470
We're going to talk about Lincoln in just a moment.

42:13.351 --> 42:14.313
So what have we raised?

42:14.333 --> 42:19.702
Well, currently we have in hand just shy of $3 million.

42:21.905 --> 42:25.091
Within the next couple months, we will hit that $3 million mark.

42:26.172 --> 42:31.922
We have commitments, all in commitments for $3.35 million.

42:32.450 --> 42:40.800
that leaves us a deficit of $1.5 million that we still need to complete the build.

42:42.141 --> 42:44.484
Now, we have already been talking with the bank.

42:44.504 --> 42:45.666
We're processing through that.

42:45.686 --> 42:53.114
The membership over a year ago already approved us taking a loan for $1.5, but I'm going to be honest with you.

42:54.256 --> 42:59.602
That's going to be a struggle because that's a big payment and I don't want

43:00.290 --> 43:03.335
an expansion to limit ministry.

43:04.838 --> 43:07.583
When we first got into this thing, we talked about ministry.

43:07.643 --> 43:11.449
And if you remember, the numbers were higher than because we included ministry aspect.

43:11.509 --> 43:14.294
We're just talking about the building today.

43:15.076 --> 43:19.543
I never want a building payment to dictate what we can do ministry.

43:20.084 --> 43:22.448
Ministry is vitally important.

43:22.468 --> 43:24.051
Ministry is why we're here.

43:24.252 --> 43:25.714
We're not here for a building.

43:26.274 --> 43:31.541
The building is just a venue that God uses so that ministry can be done.

43:32.402 --> 43:34.404
Come on, are you with me today?

43:34.604 --> 43:36.927
So we need $1.5 million.

43:37.147 --> 43:41.313
I believe that God has called us to raise that amount.

43:41.553 --> 43:44.196
But I also believe that now is the time to build.

43:45.318 --> 43:48.141
You see, we could say, well, let's just keep raising.

43:48.181 --> 43:48.922
Let's keep raising.

43:48.962 --> 43:49.723
Let's keep raising.

43:49.983 --> 43:52.687
And one day and one time we'll be able to build.

43:52.887 --> 43:55.410
But I want you to know with the cost rising,

43:55.842 --> 43:58.365
That number is going to continue to go up of what we need.

43:59.486 --> 44:02.110
It's already gone up since we started this.

44:03.611 --> 44:08.537
Now, for those of you that have been part of the 3.35 last year, you filled out commitment cards.

44:08.557 --> 44:09.398
I want to say thank you.

44:10.239 --> 44:11.501
Thank you for your faithfulness.

44:12.302 --> 44:13.483
Thank you for being a part.

44:14.184 --> 44:15.085
Don't stop now.

44:15.165 --> 44:16.467
Let's finish strong.

44:17.148 --> 44:18.289
It was a two-year commitment.

44:18.489 --> 44:19.330
Let's finish strong.

44:19.571 --> 44:20.191
How many of you know?

44:20.312 --> 44:23.215
Sometimes that last leg of the race is the hardest.

44:24.076 --> 44:24.697
You're tired.

44:24.717 --> 44:25.618
You're worn out.

44:26.114 --> 44:27.976
The devil's been going, you can't do that.

44:28.016 --> 44:28.737
You can't do that.

44:28.777 --> 44:30.279
You can't finish.

44:30.499 --> 44:31.640
You can't make it happen.

44:32.021 --> 44:33.502
But I want you to finish strong.

44:33.763 --> 44:36.766
I want you to fight the fight and do what God's called you to do.

44:36.786 --> 44:37.427
So thank you.

44:37.547 --> 44:38.889
Thank you for your faithfulness.

44:39.229 --> 44:41.111
Thank you for your continued giving.

44:41.411 --> 44:46.157
Thank you for helping us continue ministry at all three locations.

44:46.337 --> 44:48.800
Ministry is vitally important.

44:51.983 --> 44:54.226
But what we're looking at today is the building side.

44:55.138 --> 44:59.243
If you're fairly new, I would invite you to join us in this mission.

45:00.405 --> 45:01.466
This is the final push.

45:02.848 --> 45:04.971
This is the final leg of the journey.

45:05.151 --> 45:10.838
I believe that we can raise the majority, if not all, of the 1.5 million.

45:12.460 --> 45:14.042
I have felt that since day one.

45:14.082 --> 45:17.487
In fact, I asked God yesterday, I said, God, am I being naive?

45:21.552 --> 45:23.154
You know, sometimes we can be naive.

45:24.674 --> 45:27.037
But I had that question, God, am I just being naive?

45:27.578 --> 45:28.719
Is this even possible?

45:29.580 --> 45:32.103
And I just fell to my spirit, God says, I can do this.

45:33.145 --> 45:35.387
Just trust me, just trust me.

45:36.469 --> 45:42.857
And I wanted to say, well, I trust you more if you happen now, right?

45:42.877 --> 45:44.399
But I believe that God's gonna do this.

45:46.001 --> 45:51.167
If we go back to the early church, well, by the way, the more that we can raise, the less that we have to take it alone.

45:52.248 --> 45:53.650
I would rather do this debt free.

45:54.882 --> 45:58.506
We're also desiring to purchase our link and location.

45:58.526 --> 46:02.932
We've already come up with a committed price with the guy that owns the building.

46:03.853 --> 46:09.420
We've already made that agreement and I'm negotiating some things with him currently.

46:10.761 --> 46:13.645
But we'd like to buy that building in 2026 as well.

46:14.906 --> 46:21.394
The reason we didn't buy it originally is because we knew that if we had to take a loan, we didn't want to have a loan and shoot ourselves in the foot.

46:22.018 --> 46:25.024
So we're trying to be kind of proactive in that process.

46:25.926 --> 46:27.549
But we've got to raise some funds.

46:28.450 --> 46:33.701
If we go back to the early church, it's important to remember that they knew the cost, but they met the need.

46:33.901 --> 46:35.224
They rose to the challenge.

46:36.245 --> 46:40.394
For them, selling property wasn't simply spontaneous generosity.

46:40.654 --> 46:42.738
It was calculated sacrifice.

46:43.746 --> 46:45.429
They sacrificed in so many ways.

46:45.649 --> 46:47.091
They sacrificed their time.

46:47.291 --> 46:48.934
They met together each day.

46:48.954 --> 46:51.057
They sacrificed their resources.

46:51.097 --> 46:54.422
They sold what they had and they gave it to those in need.

46:54.643 --> 46:57.507
They sold or they gave of their comfort.

46:58.088 --> 47:03.777
They realized that unity and advancement was so much more important than self-gain or self-comforts.

47:05.219 --> 47:12.370
A little bit King David said in 2 Samuel, he says, I will not offer my God a sacrifice that cost me nothing.

47:13.858 --> 47:21.449
See, a sacrifice is a surrender of something of value for the sake of something or someone else.

47:22.731 --> 47:31.144
Are we willing to make a sacrifice for eternity?

47:31.164 --> 47:32.386
Our final point today is this.

47:33.968 --> 47:37.213
Building to last requires everyone building together.

47:37.233 --> 47:39.516
It will take every one of us.

47:39.596 --> 47:40.397
I said it earlier.

47:40.678 --> 47:43.442
It's not just a small handful of superstars.

47:44.738 --> 47:45.899
but we are all the church.

47:47.701 --> 47:49.382
Every location, we're in this together.

47:50.563 --> 47:56.509
Just like we were all in this together when we modified Warrensburg and did the build out in Lincoln.

47:57.430 --> 48:02.715
Just as we were all in this together when Warrensburg modified the kids' room.

48:04.116 --> 48:08.540
Just like we're gonna be all in this together with future locations when we launched down the road.

48:08.821 --> 48:13.345
We are all part of a greater family reaching this region for the cause of Christ.

48:13.505 --> 48:14.706
And we were all

48:14.978 --> 48:15.458
Devoted.

48:15.819 --> 48:16.019
Come on.

48:16.039 --> 48:17.200
That was the early church, right?

48:19.222 --> 48:21.024
It's gonna take us all.

48:21.044 --> 48:21.684
Let me be clear.

48:22.806 --> 48:27.010
When we talk about building expansion, we're not changing the mission.

48:28.051 --> 48:29.152
We're supporting the mission.

48:30.373 --> 48:33.496
We're not taking off mission areas that we support on a monthly basis.

48:33.516 --> 48:36.058
We're not limiting ministry.

48:36.078 --> 48:38.260
We're continuing all of those things.

48:38.441 --> 48:41.443
We're taking new ground for the cause of Christ.

48:41.804 --> 48:44.146
What I'm asking you in this season

48:44.482 --> 48:46.645
It's much the same that the early church faced.

48:46.946 --> 48:53.616
I'm asking you to pray intentionally what role would God have you personally or as a family?

48:53.696 --> 48:59.244
What role would God have you to do to participate in this greater calling?

49:00.186 --> 49:01.648
Don't respond at a pressure.

49:02.970 --> 49:04.392
Don't respond at a guilt.

49:05.393 --> 49:08.859
Don't respond because the person next to you responds.

49:10.081 --> 49:13.746
But respond because you feel like God is speaking to you.

49:15.394 --> 49:16.275
That's all I'm asking.

49:17.977 --> 49:20.400
I'm not asking you to do this because somebody else is.

49:21.241 --> 49:24.685
The goal is to begin to break ground the very beginning of April.

49:28.249 --> 49:29.450
This timeline is crucial.

49:29.490 --> 49:29.770
Why?

49:30.351 --> 49:32.113
Because ministry is already happening.

49:32.253 --> 49:33.975
Growth is already occurring.

49:34.336 --> 49:36.098
The question we must answer is this.

49:36.919 --> 49:40.603
How do we create space for what God is already doing?

49:42.505 --> 49:43.346
That's what we're looking at.

49:44.674 --> 49:46.997
And I believe it's gonna take a financial sacrifice.

49:47.918 --> 49:51.662
There are many of you who have already doubled what you've been giving.

49:52.002 --> 49:56.708
There are many of you who have dove into some retirement and you're giving that.

49:56.728 --> 49:58.790
There's others of you that have given sacrifice.

49:58.870 --> 50:06.098
There's some of you that are giving for the very first time you've never given before, but you felt God challenging you in this moment.

50:07.259 --> 50:08.221
I wanna encourage you.

50:10.303 --> 50:13.106
Listen to the call of God and respond.

50:14.946 --> 50:24.503
I believe that as we do this, we're making room for children to be discipled for students, to grow for adults, to be spiritually mature and for lives, to be eternally changed.

50:24.523 --> 50:32.958
So the question that we have to ask ourselves is this, do we believe that what God is building is worth the cost?

50:32.978 --> 50:37.266
If the answer is yes, then something must be done.

50:38.530 --> 50:53.606
I've shared statistics in the past, 69,000 people in our three counties alone, 20,000 in Pettis County, 39,000 in Johnson County, and 10,000 in Benton County claim no connection with God whatsoever.

50:55.428 --> 50:58.912
I believe that God's called us to build His church.

51:00.193 --> 51:01.315
So here's what we've got.

51:03.917 --> 51:08.242
In this room in Sedalia, in your seats were a card.

51:09.026 --> 51:11.829
At our locations, the ushers are coming right now.

51:11.929 --> 51:14.712
If they haven't already passed those out to you, the ushers are coming.

51:14.732 --> 51:19.418
They're going to pass those cards out to you right now at Lincoln and in Warrensburg.

51:20.379 --> 51:23.042
And this is just a modified card from last year.

51:23.462 --> 51:31.071
If you filled this out last year, this card is not for you unless God is calling you to modify what you did.

51:32.412 --> 51:37.458
But this is for anybody who has not yet been able to jump on the journey.

51:38.530 --> 51:39.231
Simple card.

51:41.535 --> 51:43.117
This is our commitment.

51:44.379 --> 51:47.364
And then has a blank, what we normally give in one year.

51:48.926 --> 51:53.032
Then there's another blank, our expanded generosity for make room.

51:53.093 --> 51:55.376
That's the make room initiative.

51:55.396 --> 51:57.119
So maybe you don't give anything right now.

51:57.920 --> 51:58.922
Maybe you're just starting.

51:59.022 --> 52:06.293
So you put zero and then a hundred bucks, thousand bucks, 10,000 bucks, a hundred thousand, a million.

52:06.413 --> 52:06.994
I don't know.

52:09.794 --> 52:11.436
1.5, we keep going.

52:15.179 --> 52:17.061
And then you add that together.

52:18.743 --> 52:24.929
What I wanna do with this, and I'll be honest, I've really toyed with how to handle this moment.

52:25.409 --> 52:29.433
In fact, I told some of the leadership this morning, I said, I don't know what I'm gonna do.

52:29.453 --> 52:32.155
I don't know how I'm gonna collect this.

52:34.458 --> 52:38.962
And I still don't, I'm still wrestling with what to do.

52:39.394 --> 52:43.480
Some of you were thinking to yourself, well, I'd really like to go home and talk to my spouse about that.

52:44.561 --> 52:45.122
And I get it.

52:45.302 --> 52:47.004
I'd really like to go home and pray about that.

52:47.765 --> 52:48.186
I get it.

52:48.606 --> 52:49.568
Some of you are like me.

52:49.588 --> 52:51.550
You're like, man, I'm one of those guys.

52:51.590 --> 52:53.633
I just kind of like jump off the cliff and then look for a rope.

52:54.935 --> 52:56.277
You know, I'm just going to trust God.

52:56.797 --> 52:57.018
Come on.

52:57.118 --> 52:58.500
Any cliff jumpers in the house?

52:58.520 --> 52:59.301
Come on, somebody.

53:00.062 --> 53:01.444
Man, we'll figure it out a little way down.

53:01.824 --> 53:03.947
We may have a few bumps and bruises if we hit rock.

53:03.967 --> 53:04.888
We'd be all right.

53:05.269 --> 53:06.130
I know where I'm going.

53:08.418 --> 53:13.163
So I want you to take this card this morning.

53:13.183 --> 53:13.844
I want to pray.

53:16.347 --> 53:17.828
And then we're gonna take just a few moments.

53:19.470 --> 53:27.840
And if you feel like you're ready to fill that card out, whether you're here or Warrensburg or Lincoln, and if you're online and you need one of these, hey, reach out to us.

53:28.621 --> 53:30.583
We'd love to chat with you on this.

53:32.325 --> 53:35.068
But again, don't give at a pressure.

53:35.909 --> 53:37.170
There's no.

53:38.242 --> 53:38.643
Pressure.

53:39.344 --> 53:42.408
If you feel like God's calling you do this, let's respond to that.

53:43.129 --> 53:48.738
That's the heart.

53:48.778 --> 53:51.341
So I want us just to pray.

53:52.824 --> 53:53.705
And then we're going to take a moment.

53:53.725 --> 53:54.847
We're going to fill this out.

53:56.449 --> 54:00.475
And then the ushers are going to come by and they're going to collect that all three locations.

54:00.495 --> 54:01.096
We're going to collect.

54:01.857 --> 54:03.680
If you feel like, Hey, I need to hold on to this.

54:04.861 --> 54:05.102
Cool.

54:06.484 --> 54:07.986
Next week, I'm going to give you an opportunity.

54:08.994 --> 54:10.976
once again to turn these things in.

54:12.178 --> 54:16.783
But if you feel like you're ready to fill one out today, I want to do that.

54:18.144 --> 54:18.244
Okay?

54:19.125 --> 54:20.507
So everybody, grab that, put that in your hand.

54:21.728 --> 54:22.409
Let's pray, Lord.

54:27.474 --> 54:29.156
Lord, speak across this room right now.

54:31.459 --> 54:32.961
Lord, speak at all three locations.

54:33.001 --> 54:34.322
Speak to those online.

54:37.410 --> 54:39.372
Look, truly, we are all in this together.

54:41.975 --> 54:43.036
We're not by ourselves.

54:43.136 --> 54:44.978
We're not attempting on our own.

54:46.760 --> 54:49.043
But Lord, we believe that You've called us to this.

54:51.165 --> 54:53.428
We believe that You've prepared us for this.

54:54.669 --> 54:56.070
We believe that You've provided.

54:56.131 --> 55:01.897
Lord, and You're going to continue because Your Word says, He who began to good work will see it to completion.

55:03.599 --> 55:04.239
Lord, You're not done.

55:04.279 --> 55:06.642
We've raised.

55:07.010 --> 55:10.615
In hand, and we'll have with the next couple months $3 million.

55:13.018 --> 55:16.121
Lord, we need another 1.5, if not more.

55:18.604 --> 55:19.626
We need money for Lincoln.

55:23.130 --> 55:23.991
Lord, would you step in?

55:26.134 --> 55:29.198
Lord, speak across this room right now.

55:31.100 --> 55:35.826
Challenge our hearts in Jesus' name,

55:36.738 --> 55:39.331
We pray.

55:39.918 --> 55:40.242
Amen.

